---
title: "Parallel Workstreams: Scrum vs Dandori"
---
gantt
    title Scrum: Parallel Workstreams (Misaligned)
    dateFormat X
    axisFormat %s

    section Design
    Research & Prototype    :des1, 0, 4
    Handoff to Sprint       :milestone, m1, 4, 0
    Revision (post-feedback):des2, 12, 3

    section Sprint
    Sprint Planning         :sp1, 4, 1
    Build                   :sp2, 5, 5
    Sprint Review           :milestone, m2, 10, 0

    section QA
    Test (after build)      :qa1, 10, 3
    Bug Reports             :milestone, m3, 13, 0

    section UAT
    Business Validation     :uat1, 13, 3
    Change Requests         :milestone, m4, 16, 0

    section Rework
    Fix QA issues           :crit, rw1, 14, 2
    Fix UAT issues          :crit, rw2, 16, 3
